edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.util
Class TileAndPrimitiveEnumerator

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.util.TileAndPrimitiveEnumerator

public class TileAndPrimitiveEnumerator
extends java.lang.Object

This class generates java files for the device package for Xilinx FPGAs to create enumerations for tile type names and primitive type names. Specifically it creates the files: PrimitiveType.java, TileType.java, Utils.java.

Author:
Chris Lavin

Method Detail

generatePartNames

private void generatePartNames()
This creates a list of parts that will give a universal list of primitive types and tile types for all the families supported (virtex4, virtex5, virtex6, spartan3a, spartan3adsp, spartan3e, spartan6).

generateAndSearchXDLRC

private boolean generateAndSearchXDLRC()
Generates XDLRC (brief reports) for the partNames in this class. Each XDLRC files is then parsed to get all tile type names as well as primitive type names.

Returns:
True if operation was successful, false otherwise.

createFiles

public boolean createFiles()
Generates the java files PrimitiveType.java, TileType.java, Utils.java. It does this based on the families specified in families. If the variable families is null, it will not create the files.

Returns:
true if it was successful in creating the 3 java files, false otherwise.
